# 📄 Software Requirements Specification (SRS)

## Mobile Salesman App

### Inventory + Sales + Order Management System

---

# 1. Introduction

## 1.1 Purpose

This document defines the software requirements for the Flutter mobile salesman application. The app follows the same backend business logic as the Laravel web system.

---

## 1.2 Technology Stack

* Mobile: Flutter
* Backend: Laravel
* Auth: Bearer Token (`X-Authorization`)
* Data Format: JSON

---

## 1.3 Core Principle

👉 **Mobile previews, backend decides**

* Mobile shows preview
* Backend calculates final values

---

# 2. API Overview

## 🔐 Auth APIs

* `POST /api/login`
* `POST /api/logout`
* `GET /api/me`

## 📦 Product APIs

* `GET /api/products`
* `GET /api/products/{id}`

## 👤 Customer APIs

* `GET /api/customers`
* `GET /api/customers/{id}`
* `POST /api/customers`

## 🧾 Order APIs

* `GET /api/orders`
* `GET /api/orders/{id}`
* `POST /api/orders`

---

# 3. Common API Rules

## Headers

```http
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
X-Authorization: Bearer {token}
```

